data.description: Roof 12/2018, AC 6/2019, Tankless Waterheater 2023,  Pavered Circular Driveway 2023, Smart Exterior Lighting 2023,  5 Bd 3 Ba, 2,885 Sqft. Rich in unique character and freshly painted in cool coastal tones with a touch of elegance!! This is such an uncommon home in the desirable Beacon Estates area of Hudson on a large corner lot... Featuring a lush richly appointed garden with a brick pavered walking paths, gorgeous arbors adorned with jasmine, tiki hut sitting area, an incredibly huge screened-in porch overlooking the backyard equipped with a large stunning water fountain, in an extremely tranquil and private setting. The inside floor plan boasts a large foyer with new Italian black & chrome doors, connected to a spacious and grand great room with cathedral ceilings and a double-sided fireplace that shows in the living room and primary bedroom. Opening up to a formal dining room and enormous air-conditioned Florida room and enclosed space that could be an additional bedroom. There are 5+ good-sized split bedrooms. Plus an additional study/office that has an added closet, could make for a 6th bedroom. The Roman Bath back corner bedroom could easily be used as an in-law suite, nursery or bonus room with it's own private porch and bathroom equipped with a Roman tub/shower. Other features include a huge walk-in shower in the owner's suite bath, a second bedroom with private office space, a third bedroom with California closets, and an impressive extra large glass-door commercial refrigerator. The roof was replaced in 2018, AC done in 2019. Storm shutters surround the house at all major openings. The primary bedroom also showcases custom display & storage for all your favorite accessories.
